"基於 Proton-GE 的 Steam 相容性工具，包含額外的修補程式以改善 VRChat 的 RTSP "
"編解碼器。"

#: src/translatables.vala:11
msgid ""
"Luxtorpeda provides Linux-native game engines for certain Windows-only games."
